The paper deals with image classification in historical documents, which is a problem that falls under the intersection of computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of deep learning methods (cs.DL) is also a major focus of the paper, as well as the evaluation of performance metrics (cs.LG). Finally, the paper deals with information retrieval (cs.IR) in the context of historical document collections.
